text:
Daniel @Haqiqatjou lies about Uthman Farooq and says he calls himself Mufti;

After Uthman denies this and calls out Daniel for lying Daniel then lies AGAIN and denies himself making the claim that Uthman calls himself Mufti.

After being caught out he corrects himself.

And by the way, these lying idiots are completely aware that I am not primarily concerned with making takfir of Saudi or not, that my issue here is what the Quran, Sunnah and Ulemah say on the matter of hukm, tahakum and tashri, before applying it to any state. So don't bother trying to distract from the issue at hand (your irjaa) by whining about modern states and trying to test people with them.

And of course, this idiot is now effectively claiming that I am a Daaeshi, when I am free from this group. I don't support any terrorist group, period. But they think everyone is as demented as them.

@jado375 @ameeniooo Allah knows you are lying murji'ah, and no joke, no deception and no idiocy you pull will change this. If He does not guide you, may He destroy you.

